      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 08:35:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于南非银行不良贷款增加，南非联合银行利润下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/absa-profit-falls-as-south-african-bank-s-bad-loans-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者信心复苏缓慢和借贷成本高企，南非联合银行集团 (Absa Group Ltd.) 的利润自 2020 年以来首次出现下滑，这家南非银行的不良贷款大幅增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/absa-profit-falls-as-south-african-bank-s-bad-loans-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 08:24:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特退出收购要约后，库里股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/elliott-walks-away-from-making-fresh-offer-for-uk-s-currys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司(Elliott Investment Management)放弃了对Currys Plc的潜在收购，导致这家英国电子零售商的股价暴跌，并为中国京东公司(JD.com Inc.)可能的收购铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/elliott-walks-away-from-making-fresh-offer-for-uk-s-currys</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威通胀放缓幅度超过食品惊喜预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/norway-core-inflation-slows-more-than-norges-bank-estimated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威的基本通胀率降至1.5年来的最低水平，重新燃起了对该国央行可能开始比计划提前降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/norway-core-inflation-slows-more-than-norges-bank-estimated</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 07:18:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
